title: Eva Cassidy - Nightbird (2015) [FLAC]
description:
Live at Blues Alley was the last album by Eva Cassidy before her death in November 1996. It was recorded in the night of January 3, 1996 at The Blues Alley, Washington D.C. - but the CD release included only an excerpt from the performance. The 2015 release Nightbird brings the complete show - 32 songs.


Eva Cassidy - Nightbird
Label: Blix Street
Format: WEB, 33 files FLAC, Album, 16bit 44.1kHz
Released: 2015
Recorded live at Blues Alley, January 3, 1996
Genre: Jazz, Blues, R&B
